INSERT INTO `notes` VALUES ('13860906784351271239970154941255', 'ddddddddddddddddddd', '', '\r\n开始写游记...\r\n<div><p class=&quot;3P&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>创建或显示字符串时，其文本必须用双引号括起，以指出字符串的开始和结束。这些双引号不会显示出来，这就提出了一个很好的问题：如果要显示双引号该怎么办呢？</p><p class=&quot;3P&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>为显示双引号，Java创建了一个特殊编码/&quot;，可放到字符串中。在字符串中遇到该编码时，将其替换为双引号。例如，请看下面的例子：</p><p class=&quot;a7&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>System.out.println(&quot;Jane Campion directed /&quot;The Piano/&quot; in 1993.&quot;);</p><p class=&quot;3P&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>这段代码显示如下内容：</p><p class=&quot;a7&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>Jane Campion directed &quot;The Piano&quot; in 1993.</p><p class=&quot;3P&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;>可以采用这种方式在字符串中插入多个特殊字符，下面列表出了这些特殊字符，注意到每个都是以反斜线（/）打头。</p><table class=&quot;MsoNormalTable&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; border=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; orphans: 2; widows: 2; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-left: 5.4pt; border-style: none;&quot;><tbody><tr><td width=&quot;280&quot; style=&quot;border-color: windowtext; border-width: 1pt; border-right-style: solid; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; border-top-style: soli